ith immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/15756/', '', 'Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Siponimod, Anakinra, More', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, Etravirine, More', 1767369485);
